<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>게시글 삭제 - SchoolHub</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/post-delete.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("partials/header", { school: typeof school !== "undefined" ? school : null }) %>
  <main class="container">
    <a href="/schools/<%= school.slug %>/posts/<%= post.id %>" class="back-link">
      ← 게시글로 돌아가기
    </a>

    <section class="delete-card">
      <span class="delete-badge">DELETE POST</span>
      <h1>게시글 삭제</h1>

      <p>
        정말로 이 게시글을 삭제하시겠습니까?<br />
        삭제한 게시글은 다시 복구할 수 없습니다.
      </p>

      <div class="delete-target">
        <strong><%= post.title %></strong>
        <span>작성자: <%= post.nickname %></span>
      </div>

      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="error-box">
          <%= error %>
        </div>
      <% } %>

      <form action="/schools/<%= school.slug %>/posts/<%= post.id %>/delete" method="POST" class="delete-form">
        <label>
          글 비밀번호
          <input type="password" name="password" required />
        </label>

        <button type="submit">삭제하기</button>
      </form>
    </section>
  </main>
  <%- include("partials/footer") %>
  <script src="/js/confirm-delete.js"></script>
</body>
</html>